No. 10-11043. Brian Lee Nestor, Petitioner v. United States. 565 U.S. 932, 132 S. Ct. 377,

181 L. Ed. 2d 238,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 6513. October 3, 2011.

Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Third Circuit denied.
